(15, 2, 'Road crash kills 3 in Ctg', 'Road crash kills 3 in Ctg', 'The deceased are Ratan Dhar, 50, Jasim Uddin, 38, and Elias, 27, reports UNB.\r\n\r\nOfficer-in-charge of Rauzan police station Kefayet Ullah said the truck hit the three-wheeler in the area around 3pm, leaving one dead on the spot and three passengers injured.\r\n', '&lt;p&gt;The deceased are Ratan Dhar, 50, Jasim Uddin, 38, and Elias, 27, reports UNB.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Officer-in-charge of Rauzan police station Kefayet Ullah said the truck hit the three-wheeler in the area around 3pm, leaving one dead on the spot and three passengers injured.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Three people were killed as a truck crashed into a CNG-run auto-rickshaw at Pahartali Badurpara in Rauzan upazila of Chittagong on Wednesday afternoon.\r\n\r\nThe deceased are Ratan Dhar, 50, Jasim Uddin, 38, and Elias, 27, reports UNB.\r\n\r\nOfficer-in-charge of Rauzan police station Kefayet Ullah said the truck hit the three-wheeler in the area around 3pm, leaving one dead on the spot and three passengers injured.\r\n\r\nOf the injured, one died on the way to hospital while another succumbed to his injuries at Chittagong Medical College Hospital, he said, adding that the injured included Rauzan Bangladesh Rural Electrification Board engineer Eliaz Hossain.\r\n', '&lt;p&gt;Three people were killed as a truck crashed into a CNG-run auto-rickshaw at Pahartali Badurpara in Rauzan upazila of Chittagong on Wednesday afternoon.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The deceased are Ratan Dhar, 50, Jasim Uddin, 38, and Elias, 27, reports UNB.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Officer-in-charge of Rauzan police station Kefayet Ullah said the truck hit the three-wheeler in the area around 3pm, leaving one dead on the spot and three passengers injured.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Of the injured, one died on the way to hospital while another succumbed to his injuries at Chittagong Medical College Hospital, he said, adding that the injured included Rauzan Bangladesh Rural Electrification Board engineer Eliaz Hossain.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, '2016-04-28 09:55:58', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL);
